data.description: Are you looking for a nice starter home on the out skirts of town that is minutes downtown Pittsburg? This 3 bed, 2 bath, with two living areas, open concept eating and kitchen, two separate carports, and is move in ready. You have two road side frontage to the property, storage building, and lots of back yard space for entertaining.  A must see, call today to schedule a showing.
